1
00:00:58,799 --> 00:00:59,640
Yan Ying.

2
00:01:00,399 --> 00:01:01,399
Don't be afraid.

3
00:01:03,439 --> 00:01:04,840
I will find a way to save you.

4
00:01:10,879 --> 00:01:11,439
Xu Chi.

5
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:13,079
What's going on with you two?

6
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,760
Why don't you go to the hospital?

7
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:15,879
Xu Chi.

8
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:17,560
Xu Chi, open the door.

9
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:19,079
Xu Chi.

10
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:33,120
It's so bad.

11
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,120
But someone still praises it.

12
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:36,199
Are you stupid?

13
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:38,199
Until Wei'an dies,

14
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,520
the literary world will never recover.

15
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,280
After reading it, I feel insulted.

16
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,439
Wei'an's mind is probably worse than a pig's.

17
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,840
No, comparing him to a pig is an insult to pigs.

18
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:31,560
Hello?

19
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,400
Ms. Xu.

20
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:32,759
Yes?

21
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,919
Xu has been out of contact for a whole day.

22
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,919
The acquisition contract from the Novel Website just came back.

23
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,159
They need him to review it urgently.

24
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,560
Can you get in touch with him?

25
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,120
He...

26
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,199
He's handling some personal matters.

27
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:46,680
Well...

28
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,080
How about this?

29
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,680
Send me the contract,

30
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,520
and I'll take a look for him.

31
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:50,120
Okay.

32
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:50,719
Alright.

33
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:51,840
Yeah.

34
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,840
Are they having a love suicide in there?

35
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,599
Xu Chi,

36
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,599
what's going on with you?

37
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:15,639
Hey.

38
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,959
what happened?

39
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:18,759
Where is Yan Ying?

40
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:23,480
Brother

41
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:24,839
Help me.

42
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,759
I can't let her leave me again.

43
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,199
How did your hand get hurt like this?

44
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,680
So,

45
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:47,240
she is really Yan Ying from Galaxy Chronicle.

46
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,480
You like a person who comes out of a book.

47
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,639
And then you plan to

48
00:04:55,079 --> 00:04:56,519
overcome the writer's block for years

49
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,360
and finish Galaxy Chronicle for her.

50
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,319
This may be the only way.

51
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:07,000
If I can rewrite the ending of Galaxy Chronicle,

52
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,040
maybe Yan Ying won't disappear.

53
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:10,120
But...

54
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,360
You were already a great writer.

55
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:25,839
Back then,

56
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:29,000
I was the one who stood in your way.

57
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,920
Maybe you could have made it through that ordeal on your own.

58
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:35,759
No one knows better than me

59
00:05:36,759 --> 00:05:38,199
your talent for writing

60
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,199
and that natural passion.

61
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,000
I'm envious

62
00:05:43,079 --> 00:05:44,160
and even a bit jealous.

63
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,720
Remember,

64
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,120
as long as you want,

65
00:05:50,399 --> 00:05:51,720
you can always be Weian.

66
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,160
It was true before,

67
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:57,079
it's true now,

68
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,959
and it will always be true.

69
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:11,199
As long as there's a chance,

70
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,399
I'll do everything I can.

71
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,279
So, tell me,

72
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:26,839
how do you want to change it?

73
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,120
I'll be your hand.

74
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,120
I want to let Yan Ying

75
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:31,519
be herself again.

76
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:33,839
But have you ever thought about

77
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,240
what would happen

78
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:36,959
if you succeeded?

79
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,959
Do you think she will stay in this world

80
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,319
or go back to her own world?

81
00:06:45,839 --> 00:06:46,959
As long as it's her choice,

82
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:48,040
no matter what decision she makes,

83
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,519
I will accept it.

84
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,480
Come on.

85
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,000
My soldiers.

86
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:00,879
Listen to me.

87
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:04,399
It's your duty to protect Qingyun State.

88
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,519
Don't be afraid of death,

89
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:08,240
or pain.

90
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,600
From the moment you join the army,

91
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,120
your faith is dedicated to the country and the people.

92
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,399
The people are behind us.

93
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,120
Your parents, children,

94
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:18,720
and friends are behind us.

95
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:19,839
From now on,

96
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,600
I will use this spear

97
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:23,639
to protect the people of Qingyun State, okay?

98
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,279
Okay.

99
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,279
Don't give up.

100
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:32,759
Yan Ying,

101
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:01,399
the war is over.

102
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:02,680
Go home.
